text: Hypatima vinculata is a moth in the family Gelechiidae. It was described by Pathania and Rose in 2003. It is found in India.Taxonomic notes on the genus Hypatima Hübner (Lepidoptera: Gelechiidae) along with a new species from India ==References== Category:Hypatima Category:Moths described in 2003
title: Hypatima vinculata
